Lammy Langle is a gnome farmer living in Hosidius. He watches over the Hosidius spirit tree patch, where players can plant spirit trees.

Contents

  • 1 Treasure Trails
  • 2 Shop
  • 3 Dialogue
  • 4 Changes

Treasure Trails[edit | edit source]

Lammy is the solution to the hard anagram clue: MY MANGLE LAL. He will give you a puzzle box.

Shop[edit | edit source]

Lammy Langle also sells basic farming tools, which can be accessed by talking to him and asking Can you sell me something? It is not an actual shop and it has no set stock; each item must be bought individually through the dialogue.
